content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 191.5 - Invoiced lots listed separately; grade and size stated

State Regulations
(a) As used in section
191.4
and this section, an
"invoice" shall mean a statement bearing the name and address of the
wholesaler, the name and address of the retailer, the date of delivery and the
grade and size of each lot of eggs. (b) Each lot of eggs covered by an invoice
must be listed separately and the grade and size for each lot stated. Notes
